奇想乐队前键盘手约翰·高斯林去世，享年 75 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-kinks-former-keyboardist-john-gosling-dies-ged-75-3478892?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-kinks-former-keyboardist-john-小鹅75岁去世Will RichardsSun, 06 Aug 2023 08:38:47 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3478892 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奇想乐队" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>戴夫·戴维斯说：“我将永远对他怀有深深的感情和爱。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-kinks-former-keyboardist-john-gosling-dies-aged-75-3478892">The Kinks 前键盘手 John Gosling 去世，享年 75 岁的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奇想乐队" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/the-kinks-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>奇想乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kinks">(Kinks</a> ) 透露，前键盘手约翰·高斯林 (John Gosling) 去世，享年 75 岁。</p><p>在网上发布的一份声明中，乐队成员雷·戴维斯 (Ray Davies) 和戴夫·戴维斯 (Dave Davies) 透露了这一消息，并向 1970 年至 1978 年间与奇想乐队 (The Kinks) 合作的乐队成员致敬。</p><p>他们写道：“我们对约翰·高斯林去世的消息深感悲痛。” “我们向约翰的妻子和家人表示哀悼。”</p><p> “向他的妻子特蕾莎和家人表示哀悼。安息吧，亲爱的约翰，”雷写道，戴夫补充道：“约翰·高斯林的去世让我深感悲痛。在与我们共事期间，他一直是奇想音乐的朋友和重要贡献者。</p><p> “向他的妻子和家人致以最深切的同情。我将永远对他怀有深深的感情和爱。伟大的音乐家和伟人。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cvh2vgugyo0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.4